{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":841,"text":"For the last 50 years,"},{"time":3047,"text":"a lot of smart, well-resourced people --\nsome of you, no doubt --"},{"time":8662,"text":"have been trying to figure out\nhow to reduce poverty"},{"time":11988,"text":"in the United States."},{"time":14180,"text":"People have created and invested\nmillions of dollars"},{"time":18168,"text":"into non-profit organizations"},{"time":20409,"text":"with the mission of helping\npeople who are poor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24249,"text":"They've created think tanks"},{"time":26159,"text":"that study issues like education,\njob creation and asset-building,"},{"time":31437,"text":"and then advocated for policies to support\nour most marginalized communities."},{"time":36736,"text":"They've written books and columns\nand given passionate speeches,"},{"time":40394,"text":"decrying the wealth gap\nthat is leaving more and more people"},{"time":44189,"text":"entrenched at the bottom end\nof the income scale."},{"time":48069,"text":"And that effort has helped."},{"time":50161,"text":"But it's not enough."},{"time":52101,"text":"Our poverty rates haven't changed\nthat much in the last 50 years,"},{"time":55858,"text":"since the War on Poverty was launched."},{"time":58576,"text":"I'm here to tell you"},{"time":60751,"text":"that we have overlooked\nthe most powerful and practical resource."},{"time":66775,"text":"Here it is:"},{"time":68509,"text":"people who are poor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71382,"text":"Up in the left-hand corner\nis Jobana, Sintia and Bertha."},{"time":75925,"text":"They met when they all had small children,"},{"time":77958,"text":"through a parenting class\nat a family resource center"},{"time":80819,"text":"in San Francisco."},{"time":82800,"text":"As they grew together\nas parents and friends,"},{"time":86443,"text":"they talked a lot about how hard it was"},{"time":88483,"text":"to make money when your kids are little."},{"time":90729,"text":"Child care is expensive,"},{"time":92435,"text":"more than they'd earn in a job."},{"time":94214,"text":"Their husbands worked,"},{"time":95398,"text":"but they wanted to contribute\nfinancially, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97898,"text":"So they hatched a plan."},{"time":99661,"text":"They started a cleaning business."},{"time":102091,"text":"They plastered neighborhoods with flyers"},{"time":104459,"text":"and handed business cards out\nto their families and friends,"},{"time":107356,"text":"and soon, they had clients calling."},{"time":109597,"text":"Two of them would clean\nthe office or house"},{"time":112686,"text":"and one of them would watch the kids."},{"time":114576,"text":"They'd rotate who'd cleaned\nand who'd watch the kids."},{"time":117515,"text":"(Laughs) It's awesome, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":119752,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":120990,"text":"And they split the money three ways."},{"time":122866,"text":"It was not a full-time gig,"},{"time":124191,"text":"no one could watch\nthe little ones all day."},{"time":126446,"text":"But it made a difference\nfor their families."},{"time":130049,"text":"Extra money to pay for bills\nwhen a husband's work hours were cut."},{"time":135100,"text":"Money to buy the kids clothes\nas they were growing."},{"time":138402,"text":"A little extra money in their pockets"},{"time":140345,"text":"to make them feel some independence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142863,"text":"Up in the top-right corner\nis Theresa and her daughter, Brianna."},{"time":147016,"text":"Brianna is one of those kids"},{"time":148955,"text":"with this sparkly, infectious,\noutgoing personality."},{"time":153789,"text":"For example, when Rosie,"},{"time":155525,"text":"a little girl who spoke only Spanish,\nmoved in next door,"},{"time":158705,"text":"Brianna, who spoke only English,"},{"time":160877,"text":"borrowed her mother's tablet\nand found a translation app"},{"time":164486,"text":"so the two of them could communicate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166290,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":167416,"text":"I know, right?"},{"time":168622,"text":"Rosie's family credits Brianna\nwith helping Rosie to learn English."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173192,"text":"A few years ago,"},{"time":175101,"text":"Brianna started to struggle academically."},{"time":178312,"text":"She was growing frustrated\nand kind of withdrawn"},{"time":182751,"text":"and acting out in class."},{"time":185023,"text":"And her mother was heartbroken\nover what was happening."},{"time":189697,"text":"Then they found out that she was going\nto have to repeat second grade"},{"time":192983,"text":"and Brianna was devastated."},{"time":195020,"text":"Her mother felt hopeless\nand overwhelmed and alone"},{"time":200215,"text":"because she knew that her daughter\nwas not getting the support she needed,"},{"time":203743,"text":"and she did not know how to help her."},{"time":205705,"text":"One afternoon, Theresa was catching up\nwith a group of friends,"},{"time":209293,"text":"and one of them said,"},{"time":210876,"text":"\"Theresa, how are you?\""},{"time":213344,"text":"And she burst into tears."},{"time":215804,"text":"After she shared her story,\none of her friends said,"},{"time":219169,"text":"\"I went through the exact same thing\nwith my son about a year ago.\""},{"time":222470,"text":"And in that moment,"},{"time":223645,"text":"Theresa realized\nthat so much of her struggle"},{"time":225926,"text":"was not having anybody\nto talk with about it."},{"time":228984,"text":"So she created a support group\nfor parents like her."},{"time":233101,"text":"The first meeting was her\nand two other people."},{"time":236459,"text":"But word spread, and soon\n20 people, 30 people"},{"time":239524,"text":"were showing up for these\nmonthly meetings that she put together."},{"time":242923,"text":"She went from feeling helpless"},{"time":245164,"text":"to realizing how capable she was\nof supporting her daughter,"},{"time":248817,"text":"with the support of other people\nwho were going through the same struggle."},{"time":252522,"text":"And Brianna is doing fantastic --\nshe's doing great academically"},{"time":255583,"text":"and socially."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257834,"text":"That in the middle is my man Baakir,"},{"time":261244,"text":"standing in front of\nBlackStar Books and Caffe,"},{"time":264113,"text":"which he runs out of part of his house."},{"time":266722,"text":"As you walk in the door,"},{"time":268321,"text":"Baakir greets you\nwith a \"Welcome black home.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":271729,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":274531,"text":"Once inside, you can order\nsome Algiers jerk chicken,"},{"time":278598,"text":"perhaps a vegan walnut burger,"},{"time":281145,"text":"or jive turkey sammich."},{"time":283519,"text":"And that's sammich -- not sandwich."},{"time":286436,"text":"You must finish your meal\nwith a buttermilk drop,"},{"time":290691,"text":"which is several steps above a donut hole"},{"time":293073,"text":"and made from a very secret family recipe."},{"time":296197,"text":"For real, it's very secret,\nhe won't tell you about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299464,"text":"But BlackStar is much more than a caf√©."},{"time":303046,"text":"For the kids in the neighborhood,"},{"time":304675,"text":"it's a place to go after school\nto get help with homework."},{"time":307704,"text":"For the grown-ups, it's where they go"},{"time":309521,"text":"to find out what's going on\nin the neighborhood"},{"time":311748,"text":"and catch up with friends."},{"time":313129,"text":"It's a performance venue."},{"time":314630,"text":"It's a home for poets,\nmusicians and artists."},{"time":318424,"text":"Baakir and his partner Nicole,"},{"time":320632,"text":"with their baby girl strapped to her back,"},{"time":322796,"text":"are there in the mix of it all,"},{"time":324374,"text":"serving up a cup of coffee,"},{"time":326469,"text":"teaching a child how to play Mancala,"},{"time":328633,"text":"or painting a sign\nfor an upcoming community event."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332182,"text":"I have worked with and learned\nfrom people just like them"},{"time":336452,"text":"for more than 20 years."},{"time":338117,"text":"I have organized\nagainst the prison system,"},{"time":340984,"text":"which impacts poor folks,"},{"time":343341,"text":"especially black, indigenous\nand Latino folks,"},{"time":345909,"text":"at an alarming rate."},{"time":347758,"text":"I have worked with young people\nwho manifest hope and promise,"},{"time":351297,"text":"despite being at the effect of racist\ndiscipline practices in their schools,"},{"time":355730,"text":"and police violence in their communities."},{"time":358605,"text":"I have learned from families"},{"time":360515,"text":"who are unleashing\ntheir ingenuity and tenacity"},{"time":364221,"text":"to collectively create\ntheir own solutions."},{"time":366435,"text":"And they're not just focused on money."},{"time":368911,"text":"They're addressing education,\nhousing, health, community --"},{"time":372631,"text":"the things that we all care about."},{"time":376260,"text":"Everywhere I go,"},{"time":377667,"text":"I see people who are broke but not broken."},{"time":381263,"text":"I see people who are struggling\nto realize their good ideas,"},{"time":385106,"text":"so that they can create\na better life for themselves,"},{"time":387698,"text":"their families, their communities."},{"time":391316,"text":"Jobana, Sintia, Bertha, Theresa\nand Baakir are the rule,"},{"time":397828,"text":"not the shiny exception."},{"time":399923,"text":"I am the exception."}]},{"cues":[{"time":402540,"text":"I was raised by a quietly fierce\nsingle mother in Rochester, New York."},{"time":407625,"text":"I was bussed to a school\nin the suburbs, from a neighborhood"},{"time":410591,"text":"that many of my classmates\nand their parents considered dangerous."},{"time":414502,"text":"At eight, I was a latchkey kid."},{"time":416933,"text":"I'd get myself home after school every day\nand do homework and chores,"},{"time":421365,"text":"and wait for my mother to come home."},{"time":423375,"text":"After school, I'd go to the corner store"},{"time":425591,"text":"and buy a can of Chef Boyardee ravioli,"},{"time":428117,"text":"which I'd heat up on the stove\nas my afternoon snack."},{"time":431145,"text":"If I had a little extra money,\nI'd buy a Hostess Fruit Pie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433976,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":435001,"text":"Cherry."},{"time":436176,"text":"Not as good as a buttermilk drop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":437854,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":438879,"text":"We were poor when I was a kid."},{"time":440597,"text":"But now, I own a home\nin a quickly gentrifying neighborhood"},{"time":444414,"text":"in Oakland, California."},{"time":446363,"text":"I've built a career."},{"time":448375,"text":"My husband is a business owner."},{"time":451605,"text":"I have a retirement account."},{"time":454305,"text":"My daughter is not even allowed\nto turn on the stove"},{"time":456906,"text":"unless there's a grown-up at home"},{"time":458509,"text":"and she doesn't have to,"},{"time":459691,"text":"because she does not have to have\nthe same kind of self-reliance"},{"time":462978,"text":"that I had to at her age."},{"time":464795,"text":"My kids' raviolis are organic"},{"time":467023,"text":"and full of things\nlike spinach and ricotta,"},{"time":469954,"text":"because I have the luxury of choice"},{"time":472301,"text":"when it comes to what my children eat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":474243,"text":"I am the exception,"},{"time":476367,"text":"not because I'm more talented than Baakir"},{"time":478723,"text":"or my mother worked any harder\nthan Jobana, Sintia or Bertha,"},{"time":482629,"text":"or cared any more than Theresa."},{"time":485395,"text":"Marginalized communities are full\nof smart, talented people,"},{"time":490525,"text":"hustling and working and innovating,"},{"time":492863,"text":"just like our most revered\nand most rewarded CEOs."},{"time":496828,"text":"They are full of people\ntapping into their resilience"},{"time":499485,"text":"to get up every day,\nget the kids off to school"},{"time":502011,"text":"and go to jobs that don't pay enough,"},{"time":504021,"text":"or get educations\nthat are putting them in debt."},{"time":506850,"text":"They are full of people applying\ntheir savvy intelligence"},{"time":511678,"text":"to stretch a minimum wage paycheck,"},{"time":514089,"text":"or balance a job and a side hustle\nto make ends meet."},{"time":517627,"text":"They are full of people\ndoing for themselves and for others,"},{"time":521426,"text":"whether it's picking up medication\nfor an elderly neighbor,"},{"time":524954,"text":"or letting a sibling borrow some money\nto pay the phone bill,"},{"time":528712,"text":"or just watching out\nfor the neighborhood kids"},{"time":530979,"text":"from the front stoop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533259,"text":"I am the exception\nbecause of luck and privilege,"},{"time":536670,"text":"not hard work."},{"time":537979,"text":"And I'm not being modest\nor self-deprecating --"},{"time":540341,"text":"I am amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541516,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":542758,"text":"But most people work hard."},{"time":544830,"text":"Hard work is the common\ndenominator in this equation,"},{"time":549023,"text":"and I'm tired of the story we tell"},{"time":551416,"text":"that hard work leads to success,"},{"time":554048,"text":"because that allows --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":555609,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556823,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":561509,"text":"... because that story allows those of us\nwho make it to believe we deserve it,"},{"time":566146,"text":"and by implication,"},{"time":567403,"text":"those who don't make it don't deserve it."},{"time":570175,"text":"We tell ourselves,\nin the back of our minds,"},{"time":572402,"text":"and sometimes in the front of our mouths,"},{"time":574701,"text":"\"There must be something a little wrong\nwith those poor people.\""},{"time":577762,"text":"We have a wide range of beliefs"},{"time":579278,"text":"about what that something wrong is."},{"time":581487,"text":"Some people tell the story\nthat poor folks are lazy freeloaders"},{"time":584795,"text":"who would cheat and lie\nto get out of an honest day's work."},{"time":588287,"text":"Others prefer the story\nthat poor people are helpless"},{"time":591224,"text":"and probably had neglectful parents\nthat didn't read to them enough,"},{"time":594529,"text":"and if they were just told what to do"},{"time":596762,"text":"and shown the right path,"},{"time":598043,"text":"they could make it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":599917,"text":"For every story I hear demonizing\nlow-income single mothers"},{"time":606080,"text":"or absentee fathers,"},{"time":607453,"text":"which is how people\nmight think of my parents,"},{"time":610219,"text":"I've got 50 that tell a different story\nabout the same people,"},{"time":615105,"text":"showing up every day and doing their best."},{"time":618491,"text":"I'm not saying that some\nof the negative stories aren't true,"},{"time":622231,"text":"but those stories allow us\nto not really see who people really are,"},{"time":628619,"text":"because they don't paint a full picture."},{"time":631249,"text":"The quarter-truths and limited\nplot lines have us convinced"},{"time":635122,"text":"that poor people are a problem\nthat needs fixing."},{"time":639570,"text":"What if we recognized\nthat what's working is the people"},{"time":643863,"text":"and what's broken is our approach?"},{"time":646441,"text":"What if we realized that the experts\nwe are looking for,"},{"time":649990,"text":"the experts we need to follow,"},{"time":651810,"text":"are poor people themselves?"},{"time":653755,"text":"What if, instead of imposing solutions,"},{"time":656782,"text":"we just added fire"},{"time":658905,"text":"to the already-burning flame\nthat they have?"},{"time":661873,"text":"Not directing --"},{"time":664054,"text":"not even empowering --"},{"time":666668,"text":"but just fueling their initiative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670000,"text":"Just north of here,"},{"time":671381,"text":"we have an example\nof what this could look like:"},{"time":674572,"text":"Silicon Valley."},{"time":676497,"text":"A whole venture capital industry\nhas grown up around the belief"},{"time":680695,"text":"that if people have good ideas\nand the desire to manifest them,"},{"time":685007,"text":"we should give them lots\nand lots and lots of money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":689028,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":690174,"text":"Right? But where is our strategy\nfor Theresa and Baakir?"},{"time":695127,"text":"There are no incubators for them,"},{"time":697447,"text":"no accelerators, no fellowships."},{"time":700577,"text":"How are Jobana, Sintia and Bertha\nreally all that different"},{"time":704276,"text":"from the Mark Zuckerbergs of the world?"},{"time":706938,"text":"Baakir has experience and a track record."},{"time":709946,"text":"I'd put my money on him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712649,"text":"So, consider this an invitation\nto rethink a flawed strategy."},{"time":720190,"text":"Let's grasp this opportunity"},{"time":722984,"text":"to let go of a tired, faulty narrative"},{"time":726825,"text":"and listen and look for true stories,"},{"time":729886,"text":"more beautifully complex stories,"},{"time":731923,"text":"about who marginalized people\nand families and communities are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":739149,"text":"I'm going to take a minute\nto speak to my people."},{"time":747986,"text":"We cannot wait"},{"time":749470,"text":"for somebody else to get it right."},{"time":753136,"text":"Let us remember what we are capable of;"},{"time":756316,"text":"all that we have built\nwith blood, sweat and dreams;"},{"time":760209,"text":"all the cogs that keep turning;"},{"time":762012,"text":"and the people kept afloat\nbecause of our backbreaking work."},{"time":765708,"text":"Let us remember that we are magic."},{"time":768677,"text":"If you need some inspiration\nto jog your memory,"},{"time":771621,"text":"read Octavia Butler's\n\"Parable of the Sower.\""},{"time":774615,"text":"Listen to Reverend King's\n\"Letter from Birmingham Jail.\""},{"time":778028,"text":"Listen to Suheir Hammad recite\n\"First Writing Since,\""},{"time":782672,"text":"or Esperanza Spalding\nperform \"Black Gold.\""},{"time":785745,"text":"Set your gaze upon the art\nof Kehinde Wiley"},{"time":788417,"text":"or Favianna Rodriguez."},{"time":790914,"text":"Look at the hands of your grandmother"},{"time":796523,"text":"or into the eyes of someone who loves you."},{"time":800386,"text":"We are magic."},{"time":803087,"text":"Individually, we don't have\na lot of wealth and power,"},{"time":805981,"text":"but collectively, we are unstoppable."},{"time":810114,"text":"And we spend a lot of our time and energy"},{"time":812409,"text":"organizing our power to demand change\nfrom systems that were not made for us."},{"time":819489,"text":"Instead of trying to alter\nthe fabric of existing ways,"},{"time":823094,"text":"let's weave and cut some fierce new cloth."},{"time":826355,"text":"Let's use some of our\nsubstantial collective power"},{"time":829869,"text":"toward inventing and bringing to life"},{"time":831865,"text":"new ways of being that work for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835423,"text":"Desmond Tutu talks\nabout the concept of ubuntu,"},{"time":840382,"text":"in the context of South Africa's\nTruth and Reconciliation process"},{"time":844061,"text":"that they embarked on after apartheid."},{"time":846378,"text":"He says it means,"},{"time":848737,"text":"\"My humanity is caught up,\nis inextricably bound up, in yours;"},{"time":854287,"text":"we belong to a bundle of life.\""},{"time":860381,"text":"A bundle of life."},{"time":864019,"text":"The Truth and Reconciliation process"},{"time":865831,"text":"started by elevating\nthe voices of the unheard."},{"time":870068,"text":"If this country is going to live up to its\npromise of liberty and justice for all,"},{"time":876033,"text":"then we need to elevate\nthe voices of our unheard,"},{"time":879146,"text":"of people like Jobana,\nSintia and Bertha,"},{"time":882651,"text":"Theresa and Baakir."},{"time":885809,"text":"We must leverage their solutions\nand their ideas."},{"time":889437,"text":"We must listen to their true stories,"},{"time":892591,"text":"their more beautifully complex stories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":895956,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":897140,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}